{"tid":1816387,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾藍絲畫畫補習社 試用期未過要員工自己比2萬蚊進修","createTime":"2020-01-08T08:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T18:35:24.000Z","uid":272518,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3b273eac4af2eab5b4cf37b1aaaedb9893b9c6f5","tid":1816387,"uid":272518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:08:23.000Z","msg":"我妹妹第一次番工就遇到無良僱主<br />\n<br />\n介紹下呢間畫畫補習社<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF1an7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF1an7c.jpg&h=f9053322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀妹番緊第2個月工<br />\n老闆就話覺得佢做唔黎 <br />\n本來試用期未過, 你咪直接同員工講話覺得唔適合囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4aneiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4aneiK.jpg&h=1f7091cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知佢就踩低我妹乜都唔識 , 嫌佢學歷低 ,<br />\n大佬, 番左先2個月見工個陣無睇CV架咩? 無啦啦話佢唔夠學歷?( 教畫畫洗唔洗一定要讀過大學呀?)<br />\n之後迫佢進修 , 叫佢讀ART COURSE<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JGmuN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JGmuN9.jpg&h=94e5a3fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哇,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 試用期都未過就要員工自己比2萬幾蚊去進修? 係咪想賺佣呀?</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n我妹緊係唔制啦, 話唔讀<br />\n點知一話唔讀, 就話我妹唔肯進修, 然後叫佢自己考慮下仲做唔做<br />\n又係咁踩佢, 話佢唔夠獨立乜乜77<br />\n重點 :  <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢話  我呢度個個員工都係自己走 我地唔會炒人既  <br />\n如果你自己辭職 我可以唔洗你比代通知金 比你即走</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講到尾 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即係唔想比代通知金 啦</span></span><br />\n我妹堅持自己無意願離職, 係公司炒佢, 要比番相應既通知期/金佢<br />\n點知個老闆要佢做夠1個月先準走<br />\n<br />\n合約 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJOsqoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJOsqoL.jpg&h=e38482a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">間公司淨係講第1個月內 同 過左3個月試用期既離職安排<br />\n得登唔寫第2個月, 想屈我妹做多1個月</span></span><br />\n仲用勞工法例大我呀妹<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母啦<br />\n好彩屋企人識下法律<br />\n呀妹比你嚇到喊<br />\n之前老闆已經話D學生係暴徒<br />\n我唔撚知你仲點做學生生意<br />\n<br />\n推埋黃色補習社圈PLZ"},{"pid":"4cfec40d70c1ed7af8cef9e8c0cb6fc8655f9bfa","tid":1816387,"uid":272518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"畫畫老師唔好做呢間野呀"},{"pid":"4037780bca1c370a74b444df1b47df5d5afbfbb4","tid":1816387,"uid":272518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"恰我呀妹不得好死"},{"pid":"daaff12ef0a7baff3681b68832d5615799b65d02","tid":1816387,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"呃錢喎<br />\n一定要推<br />\n告佢"},{"pid":"b905886b9a535d485471cc7d3aabdf2f6a9a40eb","tid":1816387,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4037780bca1c370a74b444df1b47df5d5afbfbb4","tid":1816387,"uid":272518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"恰我呀妹不得好死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"Push push <br />\n恰靚女不得好死"},{"pid":"cb47252f6e0d3ec3a6ee0e32f7fb9d098a812856","tid":1816387,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e2d3d55f40d4ca347b7aabd3bca4ca2cca5a51c","tid":1816387,"uid":272518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"有無人可以幫手推比其他畫畫老師知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36716703a54e336fd10d3e70e5d329b494230da","tid":1816387,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b905886b9a535d485471cc7d3aabdf2f6a9a40eb","tid":1816387,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4037780bca1c370a74b444df1b47df5d5afbfbb4","tid":1816387,"uid":272518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"恰我呀妹不得好死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08